title: Malaysia Capital Flows
description: Malaysia recorded a capital and financial account deficit of 14907 MYR Million in the third quarter of 2022. Capital Flows in Malaysia averaged -7738.29 MYR Million from 2005 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 51436 MYR Million in the second quarter of 2011 and a record low of -71537 MYR Million in the fourth quarter of 2008. This page provides - Malaysia Capital Flows- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Department of Statistics, Malaysia
